      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen hemolysis power-law model are standard choices for this application; selection rationale documented in the simulation plan."
