    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements table. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device design decisions; the assessment team finds the evidence package sufficient for the stated decision context.",
